spec_data.Name: python3-nose-xcover
spec_data.Description:
A companion to the built-in nose.plugins.cover,
this plugin will write out an XML coverage report to a file named coverage.xml.
It will honor all the options you pass to the `Nose coverage plugin
especially --cover-package.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 02:08:44 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Extends nose.plugins.cover to add Cobertura-style XML reports
